textBeforeTable: Below is the first ever “All Rush Team” Male and Female recipients for the 2012.  Congratulation on your achievements with Rush soccer and we wish you the best of luck as you further your career in the game. The “All Rush Team - 2012” is a program that recognizes the top senior players from all the Rush clubs around the world.  Sponsored by Eurosport and with the backing of one of Rush Soccer’s all time Elite players Todd Dunivant, each player will be recognized with a certificate and letter from Rush Soccer and Todd.  We will recognize the players on the Rush Website and hope to build Alumni of players as they progress through their soccer careers to emulate and maybe surpass the feats of some of the Rush Alumni greats such as Todd Dunivant, Conor Casey, Bobby Burling, and Jordan Angeli, along with some of the upcoming young pro’s in Danni Foxhoven and Lindsey Horan. Rush Soccer is excited to announce the latest program – All Rush Team – 2012 Last Updated on Friday, 12 October 2012 15:06
